title: PMs of Pakistan, Belgium discuss bilateral matters
content:
NEW YORK, Sep 23 (APP):Prime Minister Muhammad Shehbaz Sharif Thursday met Prime Minister of Belgium Alexander De Croo and discussed matters of mutual interest.According to the Prime Minister Office, they met on the sidelines of 77th session of United Nations General Assembly here.
